pr_body:
Pull request for GSoC 2022 project https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/T304044 : _Improvement on the custom picture selector - Make it easier for contributors to choose pictures for upload on the Commons Android app_

Reviewed by GSoC 2022 mentors Aditya and Nicolas.
